OOC: I actually created these characters and posted for them a long trime 
ago, but i forgot. But here they are again....

:::Jagger/Yusef/D'arbanville:::

::The three were walking together.  Both Jagger and Yusef kept trying to win 
D'arbanville over::
Yusef: Hey, take a listen to this.
::He takes out his acoustic guitar and starts strumming and singing::
Yusef: I listened to the wind to the wind of my soul. I'll end up where i 
think only god really knows. I sat upon the devil's lake. But-
Jagger: C'mon man! Getta load of THIS!
::He takes out an electric guitar and starts playing a familiar tune::
Jagger: I can't get no Satisfaction. I can't get no Satisfaction but i try, 
and i try, and i try, and I try. I CANT GET NO! NO NO NO! HEY HEY HEY! THAT'S 
WHAT I SAY!
::Yusef glares at Jagger, and Jagger right back at him.  D'arbanville still 
doesnt realize that her two friends are both eagerly trying to impress her.  
They walk for awhile and accidentally enter a ship that was ready to fly to 
Earth.  Before they can stop, they blast off and are headed for Earth::

--part1_166.e55f41.28d4cb31_boundary
